title: Smart Roasted Pork Tenderloin with Buttery Cauliflower-Potato Mash and Shallot Gravy
description: This classic pork dish has a new twist – cauliflower potato mash! The low carb cousin of the original but just as satisfying. Spoon aromatic shallot gravy over everything for a decadent finish.

